CommentBody: POD link sent including Carlos Mejia from R&D. Please take quality notes in case this ticket needs to be escalated to R&D.
Carlos Mejia from R&D did not attend. Please reschedule the meeting.
Carlos was able to meet with customer later in the day on 7/26. He has meeting scheduled with customer 7/30 9am ET and will provide us with an update.

Met with customer on 7/26 and 7/30 to assist with tempdb issues. Modified Schedules and disabled the Exchange solution set. Modified SharePoint group for 5 level depth with differential enabled post SP Data Drop job run. Detailed notes on the TempDB modifications can be seen in the attached word doc. From a support perspective, this should be good to close. 

Mark Richmond and James Freeman will continue communication on their end since this derives from a POC for Exchange and SharePoint.
